author: Master_Wu
title: Can't live with out it
review:
Another classic bricks set is always good to have. This set has a lot of parts for a very cheap price. It is fun and easy to make your own creations or follow the instructions to make some of the builds on the box.

I had a lot of fun with this set and I highly recommend it!

author: StevenTheBrick
title: Creative Box
review: The Black Friday Deal for this at $20 is what gives this the absolutely worth it. Even if you don't care for the builds, it gives you so much pieces to use. Parts aren't extraordinary, however. Also, along with building experience and playability.
